by safeguarding the well-being of patients and service users. <br><br>In this blog, Dr Richard Dune delves into the importance of effective CQC-regulated organisations and their significance in shaping the future of healthcare and social care in the UK.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-a213" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-dBFCZX khzvmY pf-53_ pf-color-scheme-1 pf-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-gvPcJq dRaLso"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-54_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-55_"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-56_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-57_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Elevate_Your_Team_How_Employee_Skill_Enhancement_Drives_Success_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1711538528" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Elevate_Your_Team_How_Employee_Skill_Enhancement_Drives_Success_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1711538528 1536w" width="1548" height="1179" alt="Unlocking Compliance Excellence: ComplyPlus™ Solutions for CQC-Regulated Organisations - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Unlocking Compliance Excellence: ComplyPlus™ Solutions for CQC-Regulated Organisations - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gtJxSR jkHSry pf-58_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-edLa-Dd hZPWCc pf-59_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Rawpixel Envato Elements</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-61_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-62_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-64_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-65_ pf-text-1">The CQC regulates over 30,000 health and social care providers in England alone, including hospitals and GP surgeries, care homes, and home-care agencies.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-67_ pf-text-1">According to the CQC's 2020/21 State of Care report, 87% of healthcare providers and 77% of adult social care services were rated as 'good' or 'outstanding' in terms of overall quality.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-69_ pf-text-1">In 2019/20, the CQC carried out over 22,000 inspections across various health and social care settings, highlighting the scale and scope of its regulatory activities.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-71_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-72_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-73_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key definitions</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-75_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-76_ pf-text-1"><strong>Care Quality Commission (CQC)</strong> - The independent regulator of health and social care services in England, responsible for assessing and rating providers based on standards of safety, quality, and effectiveness.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-78_ pf-text-1"><strong>Regulation</strong> - The process of monitoring, overseeing, and enforcing compliance with regulatory standards and requirements set by the CQC.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-80_ pf-text-1"><strong>Compliance</strong> - Adherence to statutory regulations, guidelines, and best practices to ensure the delivery of safe, high-quality care.</li></ul></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-82_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Care_Quality_Commission_Compliance_ComplyPlus_for_Healthcare_Regulation_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1711616109" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Care_Quality_Commission_Compliance_ComplyPlus_for_Healthcare_Regulation_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1711616109 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Navigating Care Quality Commission Compliance ComplyPlus™ for Healthcare Regulation - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Navigating Care Quality Commission Compliance ComplyPlus™ for Healthcare Regulation - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gtJxSR jkHSry pf-83_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-edLa-Dd hZPWCc pf-84_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by&nbsp;monkeybusiness&nbsp;via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-86_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-87_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Optimising_Quality_Care_ComplyPlus_Solutions_for_Social_Care_Providers_in_the_UK_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1711616494" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Optimising_Quality_Care_ComplyPlus_Solutions_for_Social_Care_Providers_in_the_UK_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1711616494 1536w" width="1000" height="1289" alt="Optimising Quality Care ComplyPlus™ Solutions for Social Care Providers in the UK - Dr Richard Dune -.jpg__PID:3efb20c0-d152-43f4-a6e2-d3edc418d2ab" title="